**Primary Endpoint**: Alpha relative power (%)
α_rel = α_power / total_power(1-40 Hz) × 100

**Secondary**: 
- Alpha peak frequency (8.5-11 Hz shift)
- Theta/alpha ratio (stress marker)
- Beta asymmetry (left vs right hemisphere)

**Safety Thresholds**:
α_rel change > +10% → duty cycle halving
θ/α ratio > 1.5 → CHEST_01 emergency pause